%nav
  .container.mx-auto
    .flex.justify-between.items-baseline.py-3
      .w-48
        %h1.text-2xl.font-bold [App Name]

      %ul.navbar
        %li= link_to 'Home', '#home', class: 'navbar__link active'
        %li= link_to 'About', '#about', class: 'navbar__link'
        %li= link_to 'Features', '#features', class: 'navbar__link'
        %li= link_to 'Benefits', '#benefits', class: 'navbar__link'
        %li= link_to 'Testimonials', '#testimonials', class: 'navbar__link'
        %li= link_to 'Pricing', '#pricing', class: 'navbar__link'
        %li= link_to 'FAQ', '#faq', class: 'navbar__link'

      %ul.navbar
        - if user_signed_in?
          %li= link_to 'Go To App', user_panel_dashboard_path, class: 'btn btn--primary'
        - else
          %li= link_to 'Sign Up', new_user_registration_path, class: 'btn btn--primary'
          %li= link_to 'Sign In', new_user_session_path, class: 'btn btn'

%header#home.bg-white
  .container.min-h-screen.mx-auto.pt-48.pb-32.px-12.relative
    %hgroup.text-center
      %h1.mb-6.text-6xl.font-extrabold.tracking-tight.leading-none.text-gray-900 Stay Organized, Stay Productive
      %h3.mb-8.text-xl.font-normal.text-gray-500.px-16 Manage your tasks effortlessly with [App Name] - your ultimate ToDo app for personal and professional productivity.

    .flex.flex-row.mb-16.justify-center.space-y-0.space-x-4
      = link_to '#', class: 'btn btn--primary' do
        .flex.items-center.gap-2
          %span Get Started for Free
          %span= tabler_icon 'arrow_right'
      = link_to '#', class: 'btn' do
        .flex.items-center.gap-2
          %span= tabler_icon 'video'
          %span Watch Video

    .flex.justify-center.mt-48
      = link_to '#about', class: 'btn btn--icon btn--primary animate-bounce' do
        = tabler_icon 'arrow_down'

%section#about.bg-white
  .container.mx-auto.py-16.px-12
    .mb-16
      %h2.mb-4.text-4xl.tracking-tight.font-extrabold.text-gray-900 What is [App Name]?

    %p.mb-16.text-gray-500.text-lg.text-gray-400 [App Name] is a simple yet powerful ToDo app designed to help you organize your day, manage your tasks, and boost your productivity. Whether you're planning your day-to-day activities, managing work projects, or creating grocery lists, [App Name] has everything you need to stay on top of your tasks and achieve your goals.

    %dl.grid.grid-cols-4.gap-8.mx-auto.text-gray-900
      .flex.flex-col.justify-content.items-center
        %dt.mb-2.text-4xl.font-extrabold 100K +
        %dd.font-light.text-gray-500 users
      .flex.flex-col.justify-content.items-center
        %dt.mb-2.text-4xl.font-extrabold 2M +
        %dd.font-light.text-gray-500 checklists
      .flex.flex-col.justify-content.items-center
        %dt.mb-2.text-4xl.font-extrabold 16M +
        %dd.font-light.text-gray-500 tasks
      .flex.flex-col.justify-content.items-center
        %dt.mb-2.text-4xl.font-extrabold ≈ 99%
        %dd.font-light.text-gray-500 satisfied users

%section#features.bg-white
  .container.mx-auto.py-16.px-12
    .mb-16
      %h2.mb-4.text-4xl.tracking-tight.font-extrabold.text-gray-900 What Makes Us Unique?

    .grid.grid-cols-3.gap-12.space-y-0
      .feature
        .feature__icon
          = tabler_icon 'app_window'
        %h4.feature__title Easy-to-Use Interface
        %p.feature__body A clean, intuitive design that makes adding, editing, and completing tasks a breeze.

      .feature
        .feature__icon
          = tabler_icon 'list_tree'
        %h4.feature__title Customizable Task Lists
        %p.feature__body Create custom task lists for every part of your life – from work projects to personal goals.

      .feature
        .feature__icon
          = tabler_icon 'bell_ringing'
        %h4.feature__title Smart Reminders and Notifications
        %p.feature__body Never miss a deadline with smart reminders that notify you based on your preferences.

      .feature
        .feature__icon
          = tabler_icon 'refresh'
        %h4.feature__title Seamless Sync Across Devices
        %p.feature__body Access your tasks anytime, anywhere with automatic sync across all your devices.

      .feature
        .feature__icon
          = tabler_icon 'table_share'
        %h4.feature__title Collaborative Features
        %p.feature__body Share lists and collaborate with family, friends, or colleagues to get things done together.

      .feature
        .feature__icon
          = tabler_icon 'progress'
        %h4.feature__title Progress Tracking
        %p.feature__body Visualize your progress with our built-in tracking and analytics tools.

-# %section#benefits.bg-white
  .container.mx-auto.py-16.px-12
    .mb-16
      %h2.mb-4.text-4xl.tracking-tight.font-extrabold.text-gray-900 Why Choose [App Name]?

    %div
      %div
        %h4 Stay Focused and Organized
        %p Prioritize your tasks, set deadlines, and stay on track with your daily goals.

      %div
        %h4 Boost Your Productivity
        %p Achieve more in less time with efficient task management and easy-to-use tools.

      %div
        %h4 Simplify Your Life
        %p One app to manage all aspects of your life, from work to personal tasks.

      %div
        %h4 Get Started Instantly
        %p No steep learning curve or complex setups – just sign up, and start organizing.

%section#testimonials.bg-white
  .container.mx-auto.py-16.px-12
    .mb-16
      %h2.mb-4.text-4xl.tracking-tight.font-extrabold.text-gray-900 Real Feedback from Users

    .mx-auto.text-center.pt-16.px-6
      %figure.testimonial
        .testimonial__icon
          = tabler_icon 'quote'
        %blockquote.testimonial__body
          %p "[App Name] has transformed the way I manage my day. It's simple, effective, and keeps me on track like never before!"
        %figcaption.testimonial__meta
          .testimonial__author
            .testimonial__name Sarah
            .testimonial__occupation Freelancer

      %figure.testimonial
        .testimonial__icon
          = tabler_icon 'quote'
        %blockquote.testimonial__body
          %p "I love the collaborative features – it's perfect for managing tasks with my team!"
        %figcaption.testimonial__meta
          .testimonial__author
            .testimonial__name David
            .testimonial__occupation Project Manager

-# %section#gallery.bg-white
  .container.mx-auto.py-16.px-12
    .mb-16
      %h2.mb-4.text-4xl.tracking-tight.font-extrabold.text-gray-900 Screenshots or Demo Video
